headline: Robinhood, Alibaba, Tesla: Trending Stocks
summary: Trading platform Robinhood's (HOOD) shares rise after the announcement that it would enter the S&P 500. Alibaba (BABA) - "China's Amazon" - is back on the radar after releasing its new artificial intelligence model. Tesla (TSLA) is now up more than 25% in 6 months amid talk of a $1 trillion pay package for Elon Musk. Join Ramzan Karmali as he breaks down today's trending tickers.
